News.Title: Latteys Industries Wins ₹187.39 Cr Solar Pump Order
News.Summary: Latteys Industries secured a major ₹187.39 crore order from MSEDCL to supply 7,369 solar water pumps across Maharashtra under the PM-KUSUM B scheme, exceeding its current market cap of ₹125 crores.

News.Title: Latteys Industries Secures ₹187.39 Cr Solar Pump Deal
News.Summary: Latteys Industries receives approval for off-grid DC solar pumps project worth ₹187.39 crores, scheduled for completion by December 2026. The company currently has a market capitalization of ₹121 crores.
